data.description:
Gorgeous completely remodeled large 3 bedroom stone and cedar sided home. Located on one of North Stonington most scenic roads just minutes to the village, I-95 as well as Misquamicut Beaches. 
Quality built home with all plaster walls and crown molding. There is a super bright kitchen with all new granite countertops, cabinets and stainless steel appliances. LP gas range for the family chef. Beautiful gleaming hardwood floors throughout as well as fully tiled bath. Walk out basement is ready to finish or leave as a workshop. There are a total of three garage stalls for the car enthusiast or weekend tinkerer. Partially cleared beautiful scenic lot ideal for livestock and large garden. New electrical service upgrade with 200 amp panel. 
Calls only between 7:00 AM and 9:00 PM Eastern and from buyers only. Absolutely No solicitation.
